guide.first: First Step: Set up company basic information
guide.departmentDes: Here you can set the company's departmental support level settings, export information, etc., to help manage the company's organizational structure.
guide.productDes: After setting the product, the male/female file and the fat pig batch can be associated with the code, and the information is also brought out by the purchase and sales.
guide.entDes: Set the company's personalized functions, all options can be turned on or off. Special reminder: Please enable [Pig House General Warehouse].
guide.warehouseDes: After setting up the company's warehouse information, you can select the entered warehouse information when you use it for materials and semen use.
guide.providerDes: After setting the company's supplier information, when purchasing pigs, you can select the entered supplier information.
guide.second: Step 2: Set up personnel information and system permissions
guide.staffDes: Maintain the company's employee information, when the employee information is created, and the production document is completed, the person who can select the document
guide.personDes: Introduce other registered users of the platform, and when completing the production documents, you can choose the person to introduce.
guide.authDes: Assign different functional permissions to different personnel under the company.
guide.farmDes: Different pig farms under the company are assigned to different personnel for management.
guide.farmSetDes: Manage all farms under the company, fill in the name, scale, person in charge and other information to complete the creation
guide.pighouseDes: Manage all the building information under the company, fill in the type, name, capacity, and person in charge information to complete the creation.
guide.boarDes: Manage all boar information, and at the same time query boar production history data, etc.
guide.sowDes: Manage all sow information, and at the same time query the sow's production history data, etc.
guide.fatDes: Prioritize setting [commodity code] to manage all fat pig batches. After the batch is created, the pigs can be managed to realize batch management.
guide.boarInitialDes: Boars in the boar file can be initialized to a house or stall, and the weight can be recorded to provide data for subsequent boar business production.
guide.sowInitialDes: The sows in the sow file can be initialized to a house or stall, and the weight can be recorded to provide data for subsequent sow business production.
guide.fatInitialDes: It is possible to initialize a batch of fat pigs to a certain house or stall, record the weight and the number of heads, and provide data for subsequent production of fat pigs.
guide.historyDes: Maintain sow breeding, pregnancy check, delivery and other information. Realize basic sow management business and provide basis for follow-up business.
